content: If the view link doesn’t work, you can also provide the direct download link, like https://drive.google.com/uc?export=download&id=[FILE_ID], but note that access might depend on file settings, and I may not always extract readable text from it. For example, for the transcript file with FILE_ID 1WKOUjkKCUUBQv7u3hlwPvTLdyTIcf1fm, use https://drive.google.com/file/d/1WKOUjkKCUUBQv7u3hlwPvTLdyTIcf1fm/view?usp=sharing.
